{"tid":1515633,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"民意如何買得起？ - 李碧華","createTime":"2019-08-29T08:48:52.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T09:28:34.000Z","uid":25558,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"881126732a86394d780a8fb9102c14cf4e37ec31","tid":1515633,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:48:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190829/20757650\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190829%2F20757650&d=sTs6EBDlf0QtlDbt2wLSRreFZk%2BLn%2Bp4m9s6a9hK%2BPA%3D&h=a11bdd9a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E6%259D%258E%25E7%25A2%25A7%25E8%258F%25AF%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20190829%2F20757650&h=1fe556f1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E6%9D%8E%E7%A2%A7%E8%8F%AF/daily/article/20190829/20757650</a><br />\n<br />\n民意如何買得起？ - 李碧華<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20190829/large/1566975760_5a92.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20190829%2Flarge%2F1566975760_5a92.jpg&h=22336d58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nYouTube截圖(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n這兩天有段片不停流傳，我們收過無數遍，轉發出去，看過了發過了又收到，一點也不覺得煩，正因人人都為他們開心，這鼓舞真是無價！<br />\n<br />\n數十名戴頭盔面罩豬嘴的黑衣人，都是同路人，在快閃示威或抗爭後，搭地鐵返沙田，經過新城市廣場回家，受到沙田友街坊分紅海英雄式夾道歡呼拍掌甚至敬禮，當時人來人往，也有一家大小吃飯shopping，全是把一切看在眼裏的小市民，沒人當他們是「暴徒」，明白年輕人為公義為香港付出血汗淚代價，采聲掌聲不斷，就是感激加感動。而黑衣人中有向街坊鞠躬回謝的，十分有禮。這紅海路程雖短，但代表了民意，他們也代表其他抗爭者領受互勉。年輕的心經歷了苦樂跌宕和團結，近千手足被濫打濫捕，是大家心頭的痛。這個夏天，全靠各人勇毅堅持，寫下一頁歷史，也讓國際矚目。<br />\n<br />\n對此另一片段，是巴士上層的乘客，離遠見到十幾個防暴警察操過，恐慌得六神無主，有人緊張大叫冷靜：「正常人唔使驚！」但仍聽得爆粗者要下車躲避。<br />\n<br />\n公道自在人心，民意最真實，無法逆轉，撐警的戲子有錢收，示威者為購裝備連飯也吃不上，「夾道歡迎」的市民，多少錢才買得起？ <br />\n<br />\n李碧華<br />\n電郵 :mcwriter@appledaily.com<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n新屋嶺輪姦疑雲 (馮睎乾)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n她親手埋葬香港 (曾志豪)"},{"pid":"b87334d75ebd7e7912feddaec2c41bba6488273e","tid":1515633,"uid":52817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:49:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0DhhYaU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0DhhYaU.jpg&h=54caa31d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"7d446b420bce5bf54614bfa97d717dd022fd1e45","tid":1515633,"uid":92836,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:49:22.000Z","msg":"毋忘聽日830香港重光紀念日。<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\"><em>830中環見<br />\n830中環見<br />\n830中環見</em></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/96PXdYs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F96PXdYs.jpg&h=2d869ee7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KF8LYC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4KF8LYC.gif&h=64c0bd73&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n［行動Post］ 830 感謝勇武暨重光紀念日行動<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1511085\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1511085</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ea5af3a407d1b080238b5b7bb3fffd7d80207337","tid":1515633,"uid":25236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:50:28.000Z","msg":"李碧華<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82fa7e761bebd2f7b93d5cf340711391219bdb66","tid":1515633,"uid":229886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T08:51:34.000Z","msg":"G7 峰會其實已經比左最後一手靚牌我地，唔跟只有輸<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/afABwfU\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/afABwfU</a><br />\n<br />\n點撚解機場行動post永遠都推唔上去？？？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/kvcDmBW\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/kvcDmBW</a>"},{"pid":"53a2eaab459a3d8429ec5a34481